            <title>[SPARK-19650] Metastore-only operations shouldn&apos;t trigger a spark job</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-19650</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We currently trigger a spark job even for simple metastore operations (&lt;tt&gt;SHOW TABLES&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;SHOW DATABASES&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;CREATE TABLE&lt;/tt&gt; etc.). Even though these otherwise get executed on a driver, it prevents a user from doing these operations on a driver-only cluster.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
